{"tid":1343864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［致抗爭者］毋忘血色炎夏，堅持到底，重光之日不遠矣！","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T22:12:58.000Z","uid":14480,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"583d59edc939c6de429e7254cfa52f3b5dfbdb94","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:43:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相信各位戰友，面對722及723，不免情緒波動，輾轉反側，徹夜難眠，<br />\n但請緊記一點，我們再次逼出政府一張牌<br />\n【鄉黑社團】<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我們懼怕，卻不放棄；<br />\n我們弱小，卻不軟弱。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwHMaai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwHMaai.jpg&h=f3afb029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回顧一下整個反送中之血色炎夏</span></span></strong><br />\n69 - 百萬遊行<br />\n612 - 武力鎮壓意圖通過送中條例<br />\n616 - 200萬+1遊行<br />\n626 - 眾籌G20登報<br />\n71 - 空城計佔立會，讀出抗爭者宣言<br />\n77 - 旺角黑夜<br />\n713 - 上水跳橋<br />\n714 - 新城市之役<br />\n722 - 上環36鎗 &amp; 元朗警黑合作<br />\n眾多運動未能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港人未忘血色炎夏</span></strong></span><br />\n先由警隊服務政權鎮壓抗爭者，再到大搞白色恐怖、高調拉人；低調放人、再設空城計試圖逆轉民意、不惜犧牲前線警員性命，再圖逆轉民意、官商合作，意圖新城市大屠殺、武力壓力未果，警黑合作，血染元朗......<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，可以見到港共政權可用之棋已不多了，緊記一點，<br />\n【寧為玉碎，不作瓦全】<br />\n【If we burn, you burn with us】<br />\n當逼到港共冇棋，香港重光之日便不遠了！<br />\n各位戰友，切勿放棄希望！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rb3rUBC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frb3rUBC.gif&h=94708128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32e3ada28f3ed8c5a80a5c9da0943f2f8a03902d","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fe41eeb0f0e0e99ba7f9f0d9cfba7a4360d18b2","tid":1343864,"uid":204817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"推 大家要繼續努力"},{"pid":"4ac74c7b37511678e5a7d5d7fef6ae415168d8ec","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe41eeb0f0e0e99ba7f9f0d9cfba7a4360d18b2","tid":1343864,"uid":204817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:48:17.000Z","msg":"推 大家要繼續努力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:50:34.000Z","msg":"可以睇到政府已無棋<br />\n只要我地堅守不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰<br />\n港共就快冇棋可行，<br />\n如果佢出老解，就係香港重光之時！"},{"pid":"b4ce83ae069e5c79d0f876447f9221d52bef8679","tid":1343864,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:03:46.000Z","msg":"連登係個暖爐, 咪再圍爐取暖<br />\n要將今日既發生<ins>全部</ins>事實真相話俾全香港知"},{"pid":"401f010a68dff48ebab8fefaf4480f44ecceac66","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ce83ae069e5c79d0f876447f9221d52bef8679","tid":1343864,"uid":263973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:03:46.000Z","msg":"連登係個暖爐, 咪再圍爐取暖<br />\n要將今日既發生<ins>全部</ins>事實真相話俾全香港知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:05:04.000Z","msg":"係要話比全世界知"},{"pid":"1f176ecf0a3daa0823a6384bd759694b8ac7523e","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efe585457e09c71ea463866aaeb001e6c705bf3e","tid":1343864,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:12:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}